-hopper            HOPPER based cards
-ipu3-cio2         Intel ipu3-cio2 driver
-ivtv              Conexant cx23416/cx23415 MPEG encoder/decoder
-ivtvfb            Conexant cx23415 framebuffer
-mantis            MANTIS based cards
